stylometry:
SUMPRODUCT- This allows you to highlite say cells B3 through B9 and C3 through C9 and get the product of all them.  
VLOOKUP- Allows you to search cells for numbers or anything you tell it in other cells.  For example, in .... cells look for the number 1 in ..... cells.  
SUMIF- Allows you to see the sum of something with the "if" statement in there.  
IF- This is just telling the computer that IF ...... cells = ....... cells place it here ect.
